# Development of Contactless Fuel Payment Card System

Prepared by:
Iradukunda Denyse

## Slide 1: Introduction
The system manages contactless fuel payments using Oracle SQL and PL/SQL.

## Slide 2: Problem
Traditional cash payments cause delays and poor transaction tracking.

## Slide 3: Objectives
- Manage customers
- Manage payment cards
- Process payments
- Store transactions

## Slide 4: Database Design
Tables:
CUSTOMER
PAYMENT_CARD
FUEL_TRANSACTION
AUDIT_LOG
HOLIDAY

## Slide 5: PL/SQL Implementation
- Procedures
- Functions
- Cursors
- Packages
- Triggers

## Slide 6: Results
The system processes payments and stores transaction records.
